@startuml svc-wildlife-tracking--post-alerts

!include ../theme.puml
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #dc2626
}

header [[/microservices/svc-wildlife-tracking/#integration-context ⬆ svc-wildlife-tracking Integration Context]]

title POST /alerts\nCreate wildlife threat alert\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with trail closure decision tree</color></size>

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-wildlife-tracking" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-wildlife-tracking/]] #F1F5F9
participant "Trail Mgmt" as Trail [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/]] #FEF3C7
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-wildlife-tracking/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-wildlife-tracking.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /alerts
activate GW #dc2626
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #dc2626

note right of Svc : Validate alert payload\n(species, threat_level, location,\nsighting_id required)\n\nClassify threat level:\nLOW | MODERATE | HIGH | CRITICAL

== Affected Trail Identification ==

Svc -> Trail : [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#get-trails-list-all-trails GET /trails]]
activate Trail #FEF3C7
Trail --> Svc : All trails with coordinates\nand active adventure bookings
deactivate Trail

note right of Svc : Geo-spatial query:\nFind trails within threat radius\n- Bear/cougar: 2 mi radius\n- Snake: 0.5 mi radius\n- Other predator: 1 mi radius

== Threat-Based Response ==

alt CRITICAL — Large predator in active area
    note right of Svc #FEE2E2 : TRAIL CLOSURE required\n- Close all trails in radius\n- Alert all active guides\n- Notify operations manager\n- Cancel pending check-ins

    Svc -> Trail : [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#post-trailstrail_id-conditions-update-trail-conditions POST /trails/{id}/conditions]]\n(for each affected trail)
    activate Trail #FEF3C7
    Trail --> Svc : Trails marked CLOSED
    deactivate Trail

else HIGH — Predator sighting, no active groups nearby
    note right of Svc #FEF3C7 : ADVISORY issued\n- Flag trails as CAUTION\n- Notify guides on duty\n- Monitor for movement

else MODERATE or LOW — Non-threatening species
    note right of Svc #D1FAE5 : LOGGED only\n- Record sighting\n- No trail impact\n- Wildlife research data
end

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO wildlife_alerts\n(alert_id, species, threat_level,\nlocation, affected_trails,\nresponse_action)
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Notifications ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Alert operations staff and active guides]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created\n(alert_id, threat_level,\naffected_trail_count, response_action)
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml
